ingredients_text:
milk chocolate 28,5% (cocoa butter, sugar, milk powder, cocoa mass, emulsifiers: lecithins [soja], flavors), fresh pasteurized milk 14,5%, sugar, caramel 11% (sweetened condensed milk, sugar, hazelnut, palm oil, flavorings), hazelnuts 10,5%, palm oil, skimmed milk powder 5,5%, wheat flour, concentrated butter, rice flour, starch, emulsifiers (mono and diglycerides) fatty acids, lecithins [soja]), flavorings, salt, raising agent:  sodium bicarbonate, thickener (tara gum) ,

of the total: milk 24,5% (fresh pasteurized milk 14,5%, skimmed milk powder and milk powder 10%),

the chocolate used is a pure cocoa butter chocolate,
ingredients_text_de: _MILCHSCHOKOLADE_ 28,5 % (Kakaobutter, Zucker, _VOLLMILCHPULVER_, Kakaomasse, Emulgator Lecithine (_SOJA_), Vanillin), frische _VOLLMILCH_ (14,5%). Zucker, _MILCHKARAMELL_ 11% ( gezuckerte _KONDENSMILCH_, Zucker, _HASELNÜSSE_, Palmöl, Aroma), _HASELNÜSSE_ (10,5%), Palmöl, _MAGERMILCHPULVER_ (5,5%), _WEIZENMEHL_, _BUTTERREINFETT_, Reismehl, Tapiokastärke, Emulgatoren: Mono - und Diglyceride von Speisefettsäuren, Lecithine (_SOJA_); Salz, Vanillin, Verdickungsmittel Tara kernmehl, Backtriebmittel Natrlumhydrogencarbonat

Milch-schokolade 28,5% (kakaobutter, zucker, milch-pulver, kakaomasse, emulgatoren: lecithine [soja], aromen), frisch pasteurisierte milch 14,5%, zucker, karamell 11% (gesüßte kondensmilch, zucker, haselnuss, palmöl, aromen), haselnüsse 10,5%, palmöl, magermilchpulver 5,5%, weizenmehl, butterfett, reismehl, stärke, emulgatoren (mono- und diglyceride) fettsäuren, lecithine [soja]), aromastoffe, salz, backtriebmittel: natriumbicarbonat; verdickungsmittel (tara-gummi).

Cioccolato al latte 28,5% (burro di cacao, zucchero, latte in polvere, massa di cacao, emulsionanti: lecitine [soja], aromi), latte fresco pastorizzato 14,5%, zucchero, caramello 11% (latte condensato zuccherato, zucchero, nocciole, olio di palma, aromi), nocciole 10,5%, olio di palma, latte scremato in polvere 5,5%, farina di frumento, burro concentrato, farina di riso, amido, emulsionanti (mono e digliceridi) acidi grassi, lecitine [soja]), aromi, sale, agente lievitante: bicarbonato di sodio; addensante (gomma di tara).
